
---

# 🚫 `.gitignore` (IMPORTANT FOR CLEAN PUSH)

```gitignore
# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Virtual environment
venv/
env/

# Flask
instance/

# Dataset (optional - remove if you WANT to upload CSV)
dataset/*.csv

# IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log

# Jupyter (if used)
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Model files (optional)
*.pkl
*.joblib